  "page": "Addam of Duskendale",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Addam\" title=\"Addam\">Addam</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Addam<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> of Duskendale</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Addam</b> was a merchant of <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a> and the subject of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/True_Account_of_Addam_of_Duskendale%27s_Journeys\" title=\"True Account of Addam of Duskendale&#39;s Journeys\">True Account of Addam of Duskendale's Journeys</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf835_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf835-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Addam_of_Duskendale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Addam visited the cities of <a href=\"/index.php/Bayasabhad\" title=\"Bayasabhad\">Bayasabhad</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Samyriana\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Samyriana\">Samyriana</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Kayakayanaya\" title=\"Kayakayanaya\">Kayakayanaya</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf835_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf835-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Addam_of_Duskendale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf835-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf835_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf835_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; Beyond the Free Cities&#32;(The Grasslands).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404093403\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.075 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.284 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 492/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10459/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4252/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 220/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 607/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.59 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  277.147      1 -total\n 85.35%  236.551      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 84.52%  234.235      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.68